Rails 2.3.5

To create a new Rails 2.3.5 app based on the Luckie Template:

  rails my_app --database=mysql --template=~/projects/jumpstart/luckie_template.rb

==========================================

Rails 3.0

To create a new Rails 3 app based on the Luckie Template:

  rails new my_app --database=mysql --template=~/projects/jumpstart/luckie_rails3_template.rb

To create a new Rails 3 app to deploy to Heroku:

  rails new some_new_app -J -T -d postgresql -m ~/projects/jumpstart/heroku_template.rb
